#. module: base_wua_pressurized_irrigation_request
#: model:mail.template,body_html:base_wua_pressurized_irrigation_request.wua_preswatering_weekly_email_template
msgid "\n"
"                \n"
"                    <p>Dear <strong>${object.name}</strong>,</p>\n"
"                    <p>We are pleased to provide your watering schedule for the upcoming week. Below are the details for your scheduled consumptions:</p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <table border=\"1\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; text-align: left;\">\n"
"                        <thead>\n"
"                            <tr style=\"background-color: #f2f2f2;\">\n"
"                                <th style=\"padding: 8px;\">Date</th>\n"
"                                <th style=\"padding: 8px;\">Water Connection</th>\n"
"                                <th style=\"padding: 8px;\">Nominal Flow (l/s)</th>\n"
"                                <th style=\"padding: 8px;\">Duration (h)</th>\n"
"                                <th style=\"padding: 8px;\">Volume (m³)</th>\n"
"                            </tr>\n"
"                        </thead>\n"
"                        <tbody>\n"
"                            % for consumption in ctx['data']['consumptions']:\n"
"                                <tr>\n"
"                                    <td style=\"padding: 8px;\">${consumption.get('date', '-')}</td>\n"
"                                    <td style=\"padding: 8px;\">${consumption.get('water_connection', '-')}</td>\n"
"                                    <td style=\"padding: 8px;\">${consumption.get('nominal_flow', '0.0')}</td>\n"
"                                    <td style=\"padding: 8px;\">${consumption.get('watering_duration', '0')}</td>\n"
"                                    <td style=\"padding: 8px;\">${consumption.get('watering_volume', '0.0')}</td>\n"
"                                </tr>\n"
"                            % endfor\n"
"                        </tbody>\n"
"                    </table>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please do not hesitate to contact us.</p>\n"
"                    <p>Best regards,<br>Your Water Authority Team</p>\n"
"                \n"
"            "
msgstr "\n"
"                \n"
"                    <p>Estimado/a <strong>${object.name}</strong>,</p>\n"
"                    <p>Nos complace proporcionarle su calendario de riego para la próxima semana. A continuación, encontrará los detalles de sus consumos programados:</p>\n"
"\n"
"                    <table border=\"1\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; text-align: left;\">\n"
"                        <thead>\n"
"                            <tr style=\"background-color: #f2f2f2;\">\n"
"                                <th style=\"padding: 8px;\">Fecha</th>\n"
"                                <th style=\"padding: 8px;\">Toma</th>\n"
"                                <th style=\"padding: 8px;\">Caudal Nominal (l/s)</th>\n"
"                                <th style=\"padding: 8px;\">Duración (h)</th>\n"
"                                <th style=\"padding: 8px;\">Volumen (m³)</th>\n"
"                            </tr>\n"
"                        </thead>\n"
"                        <tbody>\n"
"                            % for consumption in ctx['data']['consumptions']:\n"
"                                <tr>\n"
"                                    <td style=\"padding: 8px;\">${consumption.get('date', '-')}</td>\n"
"                                    <td style=\"padding: 8px;\">${consumption.get('water_connection', '-')}</td>\n"
"                                    <td style=\"padding: 8px;\">${consumption.get('nominal_flow', '0.0')}</td>\n"
"                                    <td style=\"padding: 8px;\">${consumption.get('watering_duration', '0')}</td>\n"
"                                    <td style=\"padding: 8px;\">${consumption.get('watering_volume', '0.0')}</td>\n"
"                                </tr>\n"
"                            % endfor\n"
"                        </tbody>\n"
"                    </table>\n"
"\n"
"                    <p>Si tiene alguna pregunta o necesita asistencia, no dude en ponerse en contacto con nosotros.</p>\n"
"                \n"
"            "

